data.description: $20,000 PRICE REDUCTION + $7,500 RATE BUY DOWN CREDIT - HELPING YOU HAVE HUNDREDS ON YOUR MONTHLY PAYMENT!!!!!  MOTIVATED SELLERS!!! Located in the West Ridge Subdivision, providing a quick commute to Fort Liberty, Raleigh, and Moore County + schools, grocery, and shopping! 3 Bedrooms + a MASSIVE Bonus Room, 2.5 Bathrooms! Covered front porch welcomes you into the Great Room where you'll find a shiplap gas log fireplace! Kitchen with breakfast area, breakfast bar, ss appliances, custom cabinetry and pantry! Formal Dining Room off from entryway! 1/2 bath completes the main floor! All bedrooms upstairs! Owners Suite with  trey ceiling, large WIC, soaking tub with relaxing chandelier fixture above, walk-in shower! 2 other large bedrooms, full bathroom, and laundry closet! Huge Bonus Room can make a great office, library, game room, man cave, etc! Spacious yard with large deck to enjoy!
